# KiwiSense V1 PCB

## Overview

KiwiSense V1 is currently implemented as a breadboard prototype for rapid development and testing.

A custom PCB is planned for a future revision to improve reliability, reduce wiring complexity, and simplify assembly.

## Planned Improvements

- Compact PCB layout
- Screw terminal connectors
- Improved power distribution
- Sensor headers
- Mounting holes
- Better cable management

## Current Status

- Breadboard Prototype ✅
- PCB Design ⏳ Planned for Version 2
